{"tid":1180671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾國斌：反修例遊行難令自由黨重演23條倒戈","createTime":"2019-06-01T04:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T16:01:53.000Z","uid":254461,"like":1,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b41d2b59a8c8b30fdfa7efc15a0cc6812bf9780d","tid":1180671,"uid":254461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:22:29.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】自由黨黨魁鍾國斌在本台節目《大鳴大放》指，接受政府提出的逃犯條例的讓步方案，但認為在刑事相互法律協助仍有細節釐清，又指即使幾十萬人遊行反修例，<span style=\"color: red;\">自由黨轉投反對票的機會不大</span>。<br />\n<br />\n建制派發表聯署後，政府再就逃犯條例修訂讓步。參與聯署的自由黨黨魁鍾國斌在本台節目《大鳴大放》指，將移交門檻提高至7年刑期的嚴重罪行<span style=\"color: red;\">足以釋除商界疑慮</span>，但認為刑事調查、凍結資產等相互法律協助上仍有細節釐清。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，<span style=\"color: red;\">由中央機關即最高人民檢察院提出移交申請，可讓港商安心</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。泛民連日呼籲市民本月9日遊行反修例，今次遊行會否令自由黨23條倒戈的一幕重演。<span style=\"color: red;\">不少外商反修例是基於誤解</span> ，相信條例通過不會引發撤資潮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088f25717e5c7d86f54c0a4cd28affb47e5fd1a4","tid":1180671,"uid":254461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e185d1bfa9cd101a3ce877e9e7d8bce97a62e3d3","tid":1180671,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:59:42.000Z","msg":"其實佢既然都話外面啲人誤解，即係佢理解個條例，咁政府班人唔敢出來同人再傾，可以叫佢出來比其他唔明嘅人查問下究竟佢哋理解咗啲咩。"},{"pid":"4783c6e09113e79b7ae52e1681caade2d294d7b6","tid":1180671,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>JAVA<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJAVA<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nJAVA<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6e08a07f6fae5d2ddc2aeb1c0c1677aea1cbdf76","tid":1180671,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:09:07.000Z","msg":"棄權呢？等埋發叔？"},{"pid":"b333b316a41200542d3178e8b466442c531745cf","tid":1180671,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"可讓港商安心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcf4088bb3163d9b915ac583034c21ac3481708","tid":1180671,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"你估個個好似田少咁有骨氣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83062ebdb9358d6e6ed100c096f7e664a543eafe","tid":1180671,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/80JHoKe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F80JHoKe.png&h=e52ac0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地田大少唔係咁講喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d11fac8e276c5fd56ac49c5e422dbf9b2730b17","tid":1180671,"uid":192068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:18:37.000Z","msg":"認真想問<br />\n上次23條倒戈，係有提早出聲，定係投票果刻先倒戈？<br />\n今次有冇可能係扮支持，去到投票果刻先否決送中？"},{"pid":"d4888e4c89aa1b253a8ca8f21d153824c33d3cb6","tid":1180671,"uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:22:33.000Z","msg":"而家個自由黨已經唔係2003嗰個<br />\n不過都會照出<br />\n越多人，外國施壓就越大<br />\n再送多啲子彈畀侵侵"},{"pid":"d93c2f8ef3b4cf265e588cb71b46f080fe0dbb38","tid":1180671,"uid":254461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4d11fac8e276c5fd56ac49c5e422dbf9b2730b17","tid":1180